sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant RA as RA (Coordinator)
    participant CA as CA (Context)
    participant EA as EA (Execution)
    participant IA as IA (Integration)
    participant MA as MA (Monitoring)
    participant OA as OA (Optimization)
    participant VA as VA (Validation)

    U->>RA: Submit task
    RA->>CA: Build context package
    CA-->>RA: Context bundle

    RA->>EA: Execute plan with context
    EA-->>RA: Raw execution result

    RA->>IA: Integrate outputs and dependencies
    IA-->>RA: Integrated result

    par Runtime visibility
        RA->>MA: Request runtime telemetry
        MA-->>RA: Health and signal metrics
    and Quality gate
        RA->>VA: Validate integrated result
        VA-->>RA: Pass/Fail + findings
    end

    alt Validation failed
        RA->>OA: Request optimization strategy
        OA-->>RA: Optimization hints
        RA->>EA: Re-run with optimized parameters
        EA-->>RA: New execution result
        RA->>IA: Re-integrate
        IA-->>RA: Updated integrated result
        RA->>VA: Re-validate
        VA-->>RA: Pass
    else Validation passed
        Note over RA,VA: First-pass success
    end

    RA-->>U: Final verified result